reviewText: My kids love Bill Nye and they learn a lot from these videos.
I order a lot of books for the school library.  When they are new books the quality is perfect.  This is the first time I ordered a DVD.  It looks like it is I. Perfect shape.

I needed something quick to do with my 6th grade class.
I was going to have a substitute in for the day and I wanted something that went with the lesson, kept the students attention and was easy for the sub.
The video was perfect and I got my video within two days, so I could preview and prepare a study guide with an answer key for the substitute.
